      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AVA'S MILO (6) could manage only third but ran handy time (19.65) at this track over 340m. Has the ability and looks hard to top. PANDA UNLEASHED (5) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at Dubbo over 516m behind Gemma Keeping (30.53) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Should play a prominent role. IMPERIAL AUDREY (4) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last time finished 2nd in a Grade 5 on February 25 over 431m at this track behind Mr. Speckle beaten 0.8 lengths (25.03). Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Overdue and gets her chance. BORN FEARLESS (2) has strong claims after a top-three finish last time out.",
